        "Respected Sir,",
        "Writing this letter to describe my dissatisfaction about a product of your brand I bought from an online shopping website.",
        "I ordered one of Bluetooth Headphones in your SONY WIO series from the Amazon on fourteenth of April and received it on eightieth i.e. two days before in a good condition.",
